{"entity":{"id":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","type":"chapter","slug":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","label":"Hos.11","rawId":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","book":{"id":"rect9laYKg0Xd0Uzg","type":"book","slug":"hos","label":"Hosea","subtitle":"Minor Prophets","count":197,"description":"14 chapters, 95 people, 44 places"}},"stats":{"verses":12,"people":2,"places":4,"events":1},"nodes":[{"id":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Hos.11","slug":"hos_11","score":12},{"id":"rect9laYKg0Xd0Uzg","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Hosea","slug":"hos","score":197},{"id":"recEtv9ql7Hh4XAW4","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Ephraim","slug":"ephraim_1206","score":4},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":4},{"id":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Egypt","slug":"egypt_362","score":3},{"id":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Assyria","slug":"assyria_111","score":2},{"id":"recqAEHPEI3gAP9H8","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Admah","slug":"admah_27","score":1},{"id":"rec4vcolAuZ1BVvOs","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Zeboiim","slug":"zeboiim_1244","score":1},{"id":"recekTocE5mIkvDEk","type":"event","group":"event","label":"Prophecies of Hosea","slug":"event-206","score":12}],"links":[{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"rect9laYKg0Xd0Uzg","label":"part of"},{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"recEtv9ql7Hh4XAW4","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"recqAEHPEI3gAP9H8","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"rec4vcolAuZ1BVvOs","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recMxvMdUtYMo4Azu","target":"recekTocE5mIkvDEk","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recf45dUKeKOQLOC9","ref":"Hos.11.1","text":"When Israel was a child, then I loved him, and called my son out of Egypt.","year":-740},{"id":"recXjyzIBnCVGvjow","ref":"Hos.11.2","text":"As they called them, so they went from them: they sacrificed unto Baalim, and burned incense to graven images.","year":-740},{"id":"recp0n5QUwxmyct3j","ref":"Hos.11.3","text":"I taught Ephraim also to go, taking them by their arms; but they knew not that I healed them.","year":-740},{"id":"recXlsWPT89H6jS6O","ref":"Hos.11.4","text":"I drew them with cords of a man, with bands of love: and I was to them as they that take off the yoke on their jaws, and I laid meat unto them.","year":-740},{"id":"recTt8tZGedNr9Dpx","ref":"Hos.11.5","text":"He shall not return into the land of Egypt, but the Assyrian shall be his king, because they refused to return.","year":-740},{"id":"receUMH44aekmIKnI","ref":"Hos.11.6","text":"And the sword shall abide on his cities, and shall consume his branches, and devour them, because of their own counsels.","year":-740},{"id":"rectNbP9Bp4v89Awc","ref":"Hos.11.7","text":"And my people are bent to backsliding from me: though they called them to the most High, none at all would exalt him.","year":-740},{"id":"recqj2bCqlmn0SRBt","ref":"Hos.11.8","text":"How shall I give thee up, Ephraim? how shall I deliver thee, Israel? how shall I make thee as Admah? how shall I set thee as Zeboim? mine heart is turned within me, my repentings are kindled together.","year":-740}]}
